          <h2 class="games-column-header">Universal Paperclips</h2>
          <div class="text-container" id="games-text-container">
            <p class="games-column-text">Start with a single paperclip—and end with the fate of the universe. This minimalist strategy game slowly unfolds into a complex simulation of automation, economics, and AI decision-making. As you scale production and delegate control to algorithms, you’ll experience firsthand how small optimizations can snowball into massive, often unintended, consequences.</p>
            <p class="games-column-text">Perfect for STEM majors, Universal Paperclips offers more than entertainment—it models real-world systems thinking, resource management, and exponential growth in a hands-on way. It’s a compelling reminder of how innovation, once set in motion, can shape outcomes far beyond its original scope.</p>
          </div>
          {{> components/buttons/mark-done-button taskID="1" taskType="game" link="https://www.decisionproblem.com/paperclips/index2.html" button-text="Play Now"}}
        </div>

